reviews.review_text: Great Audience Recording! Wonderful recording...I like it better than the Sennheiser>Sony PCM1. Pretty good performance, and Jerry forgets the lyrics to Shakedown.

Rango Keshavan the Miller of auds now that CM has worked his magic on several of Rango's auds, people should notice that Mr. Keshavan's work deserves as much praise as the vaunted Mr. Miller. check out all of Rango's work. these auds are better than or equal to a matrix, full range of sound, plus he picks up the nuances that us boards lovers crave. you can always feel Phil, hear a string bend on an ibeneze or a travis bean,  catch that lilt in the voice and not be over whelmed by the crowd. plus i am never left with my ears ringing from the crowd or too much treble. that is a big deal to someone that has  titenitis (ringing of the ears) 
  Rango Keshavan is the Charlie Miller of auds!
 as for this performance, and being at the Greek, if i could stand in front of the boys and see this very concert today, how could i not give it a five, and Rango transports you there.
